cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.DS

Reasoning: The paper deals with the problem of repairing models and programs, which involves logical reasoning and constraint solving. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The paper also uses SAT solving, which falls under cs.PL (Programming Languages). The extension of the method to repair concurrent programs suggests that it could also belong to cs.SE (Software Engineering). The use of boolean constraints and the NP-completeness result suggest a connection to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
